01:09:39,475 --> 01:09:40,317
Let's move.

772
01:09:45,881 --> 01:09:49,556
We'll be back. I hope, next time,
you have some answers for us.

773
01:09:54,557 --> 01:09:56,093
Reyes, stay here.

774
01:09:56,759 --> 01:09:57,737
Yes, Sir.

775
01:10:02,998 --> 01:10:04,102
Rommel?

776
01:10:26,255 --> 01:10:30,465
This is not real.
Rommel is alive. He's alive.

777
01:10:35,965 --> 01:10:36,875
Hello.

778
01:10:36,932 --> 01:10:39,310
Rudolf. Rudolf, you lied to me.

779
01:10:40,302 --> 01:10:43,749
Tell me the truth.
I know you were with my son last night.

780
01:10:44,006 --> 01:10:45,986
Tell me what happened.

781
01:10:46,475 --> 01:10:47,385
Who told you?

782
01:10:47,743 --> 01:10:48,721
Rommel.

783
01:10:49,345 --> 01:10:52,883
Weren't you all together last night?
You, Glen and William.

784
01:10:53,315 --> 01:10:56,524
And now Glen is dead, correct?

785
01:10:57,152 --> 01:10:58,631
Rudolf, listen.

786
01:10:59,955 --> 01:11:03,300
You'll all rot in jail
unless you tell me the truth.

787
01:11:03,525 --> 01:11:05,630
Tell me what happened!

788
01:11:09,965 --> 01:11:11,467
Why don't you ask your son?

789
01:11:12,468 --> 01:11:14,539
He raped and killed Amanda.

790
01:11:14,870 --> 01:11:17,714
Go ahead, try to turn us in.

791
01:11:18,040 --> 01:11:21,249
You better hide your son
because I'm coming for him.

792
01:11:21,610 --> 01:11:26,116
And if you insist on messing with us,
I'll kill you next.

793
01:11:26,582 --> 01:11:28,528
You can't do that to my son.

794
01:11:29,251 --> 01:11:33,996
He didn't do anything, Rudolf.
You can't hurt my son.

795
01:11:36,258 --> 01:11:37,293
Rudolf!

796
01:11:40,095 --> 01:11:41,073
Oh, God.

797
01:11:46,368 --> 01:11:48,507
Dude, Rommel's alive.

798
01:11:48,871 --> 01:11:50,748
He was able to talk to his mother.

799
01:11:50,973 --> 01:11:52,145
We're dead.

800
01:11:53,676 --> 01:11:56,623
That bastard.
He must have killed Glen.

801
01:11:57,913 --> 01:12:00,723
What? Are you sure?

802
01:12:01,116 --> 01:12:03,619
I don't think Rommel did this.
Have you seen Glen's face?

803
01:12:03,852 --> 01:12:05,160
Must have seen a ghost
or something.

804
01:12:05,387 --> 01:12:06,889
Since when did you believe in ghosts?

805
01:12:10,859 --> 01:12:12,839
Where could he have hidden?

806
01:12:15,397 --> 01:12:17,399
Maybe he went to the cops, Bro.

807
01:12:18,067 --> 01:12:19,512
We're dead, man.

808
01:12:23,739 --> 01:12:25,946
Then let the cops look for him first.

809
01:12:27,409 --> 01:12:29,855
Here's what you're gonna do.
Here's Amanda's cellphone.

810
01:12:30,079 --> 01:12:31,524
Take this to the police station.

811
01:12:34,750 --> 01:12:36,161
Why me? You do it.

812
01:12:37,686 --> 01:12:40,030
Are you stupid? Don't be a pussy.

813
01:12:41,457 --> 01:12:43,528
I still need to clean the evidence --

814
01:12:44,293 --> 01:12:47,331
Rommel and his mother.
No witnesses.

815
01:12:49,198 --> 01:12:50,176
Go.

816
01:12:56,472 --> 01:12:57,382
Dude.

817
01:13:05,547 --> 01:13:07,220
Rudolf.

818
01:13:08,183 --> 01:13:10,220
Rudolf.

819
01:13:37,045 --> 01:13:40,515
Hey! Hey! Watch it, asshole!

820
01:13:59,001 --> 01:13:59,979
Ma'am.

821
01:14:00,469 --> 01:14:02,107
I thought you left?

822
01:14:02,471 --> 01:14:04,382
They made me stay to watch you.

823
01:14:05,941 --> 01:14:07,682
I have something to tell you.

824
01:14:08,310 --> 01:14:11,223
Rudolf was just found dead.
Hit-and-run.

825
01:14:11,280 --> 01:14:16,559
Ma'am, if you know where your son is,
it's best you turn him over to us.

826
01:14:17,352 --> 01:14:22,028
Because the killer is
targeting all our suspects.

827
01:14:22,558 --> 01:14:24,970
Rommel might be next.

828
01:14:25,060 --> 01:14:27,472
My son didn't do anything.

829
01:14:30,499 --> 01:14:31,773
I'm sorry to do this, Ma'am.

830
01:14:32,501 --> 01:14:36,472
But we got this phone
from Rudolf s pocket.

831
01:14:38,307 --> 01:14:40,947
Listen carefully to this
piece of evidence...

832
01:14:41,009 --> 01:14:43,421
connecting your son to all of this.

833
01:14:44,112 --> 01:14:46,058
You son of a bitch, Glen.

834
01:14:47,616 --> 01:14:49,618
Do you really need
to threaten me like that?

835
01:14:50,385 --> 01:14:52,865
This is a blessing.

836
01:14:53,689 --> 01:14:55,168
Why would I refuse it?

837
01:14:58,994 --> 01:15:00,200
You're too slow.

838
01:15:01,463 --> 01:15:07,436
Believe it or not, they're being
murdered by a female ghost.

839
01:15:07,503 --> 01:15:11,383
And if your son is a rapist
and a killer, he's next.

840
01:15:11,640 --> 01:15:14,382
Better turn in Rommel
so we can protect him.

841
01:15:20,983 --> 01:15:22,121
Rommel.

842
01:15:25,454 --> 01:15:27,229
Sir, with all due respect, sir...

843
01:15:27,756 --> 01:15:29,997
I don't think you shouldn't have
threatened Mrs. Calderon...

844
01:15:30,058 --> 01:15:31,662
to give up his son.

845
01:15:31,727 --> 01:15:33,638
Assuming she is hiding him...

846
01:15:33,695 --> 01:15:37,871
we're not even sure he's behind
all of this, are we, Sir?

847
01:15:37,966 --> 01:15:40,503
I wasn't scaring her.

848
01:15:41,069 --> 01:15:44,016
I was giving her a chance
to say goodbye to him...

849
01:15:44,072 --> 01:15:46,575
...because I'm certain
Rommel will be next.

850
01:15:47,509 --> 01:15:48,920
Who's gonna kill him, Sir?

851
01:15:51,713 --> 01:15:55,490
Oh no, Sir!
It might be the ghost, right?

852
01:15:55,551 --> 01:15:58,532
The urban legend in this area.

853
01:15:58,587 --> 01:16:00,191
We're doomed, Sir!

854
01:16:01,156 --> 01:16:02,100
Are you mocking me?

855
01:16:02,224 --> 01:16:04,568
- You're mocking me?
- Sir. Sir, let go.

856
01:16:11,133 --> 01:16:12,874
Don't go with Jerry.

857
01:16:24,546 --> 01:16:26,048
The other side!

858
01:16:30,419 --> 01:16:31,397
Get her!

859
01:17:05,587 --> 01:17:06,497
Sandra!

860
01:17:10,359 --> 01:17:11,497
Choose!

861
01:17:13,428 --> 01:17:17,308
Either you come out
or We kill this kid?

862
01:17:20,102 --> 01:17:23,242
Sandra, don't come out.

863
01:17:24,172 --> 01:17:25,150
Shut the hell up!

864
01:17:27,976 --> 01:17:32,447
- Think about it, Sandra.
- Jun.

865
01:17:33,081 --> 01:17:38,155
- Jun.
- One! Two! Three!

866
01:17:38,587 --> 01:17:39,964
- Jun.
- Four!

867
01:17:40,922 --> 01:17:47,771
Five! Six! Seven! Eight!

868
01:17:54,069 --> 01:17:55,548
I knew you'd come out.

869
01:17:55,804 --> 01:17:57,909
You shouldn't have make us run
after you. Save us the trouble.

870
01:18:11,386 --> 01:18:13,366
Please, Jerry!

871
01:18:15,123 --> 01:18:17,729
Jerry, please don't do this.

872
01:18:23,465 --> 01:18:25,843
Stop! Jun.

873
01:18:28,003 --> 01:18:29,414
Jerry!

874
01:18:30,205 --> 01:18:35,621
Let me go! Please, let me go!

875
01:18:40,916 --> 01:18:42,259
I was helpless.

876
01:18:43,151 --> 01:18:44,186
Sir?

877
01:18:46,288 --> 01:18:47,926
Let's search the forest.

878
01:18:51,159 --> 01:18:53,196
I know where we'll find the girl.

879
01:20:23,819 --> 01:20:24,729
Son?

880
01:20:42,137 --> 01:20:43,115
Rommel?

881
01:20:58,353 --> 01:20:59,423
Rommel?

882
01:21:09,798 --> 01:21:10,708
Rommel.

883
01:21:13,068 --> 01:21:14,012
Rommel.

884
01:21:14,870 --> 01:21:18,340
How is your wound, Rommel?

885
01:21:18,406 --> 01:21:19,817
How did you manage to hide
from the cops?

886
01:21:19,975 --> 01:21:21,386
Big brother helped me.

887
01:21:22,978 --> 01:21:28,951
He blocked all the statues
so the Police wouldn't see me.

888
01:21:32,854 --> 01:21:34,197
Let's go, Rommel.

889
01:21:36,491 --> 01:21:38,596
William might be looking for you.

890
01:21:40,495 --> 01:21:43,601
Rudolf and Glen are gone.

891
01:21:43,999 --> 01:21:47,310
They were killed. You might be next.

892
01:21:49,104 --> 01:21:54,019
I'm innocent. I didn't do anything.

893
01:21:54,075 --> 01:21:55,110
Rommel.

894
01:21:57,779 --> 01:22:02,194
Just tell me what really happened...

895
01:22:02,250 --> 01:22:09,725
so that I will know what to believe.

896
01:22:11,593 --> 01:22:12,833
Mom.

897
01:22:17,666 --> 01:22:19,668
Don't you love me anymore?

898
01:22:23,338 --> 01:22:26,217
Do I need to get sick?

899
01:22:32,380 --> 01:22:37,227
I heard you during the accident...

900
01:22:41,957 --> 01:22:44,198
choosing Amiel to be saved.

901
01:22:46,094 --> 01:22:48,540
- Not me.
- That's not true.

902
01:22:50,832 --> 01:22:54,177
When will you choose me?

903
01:22:57,839 --> 01:23:00,342
Rommel, I didn't choose.

904
01:23:02,310 --> 01:23:04,517
I never chose
between the two of you.

905
01:23:04,579 --> 01:23:08,459
I love you both as your mother.

906
01:23:09,985 --> 01:23:18,131
That day, I called for him first
since I was used to...

907
01:23:18,994 --> 01:23:23,067
taking care of him first because...

908
01:23:23,765 --> 01:23:30,410
I blamed myself for his blindness.

909
01:23:32,140 --> 01:23:34,416
But you, Rommel...

910
01:23:34,476 --> 01:23:40,222
you were always so loving.

911
01:23:40,281 --> 01:23:44,696
I always expected you
to understand.

912
01:23:45,487 --> 01:23:51,597
I never realized I was neglecting you.
I didn't know.

913
01:23:52,394 --> 01:23:55,500
I'm sorry, Son.

914
01:23:56,798 --> 01:24:00,245
I'm sorry. Forgive me.

915
01:24:03,405 --> 01:24:06,545
Please, forgive you mother.

916
01:24:18,219 --> 01:24:19,857
I'm also sorry, Mom.

917
01:24:31,332 --> 01:24:35,747
Mom, we need to find Amanda.

918
01:24:39,174 --> 01:24:40,653
All right.

919
01:24:43,311 --> 01:24:44,619
Come on.

920
01:24:50,018 --> 01:24:53,989
Just a little further, son.
Let's just get past the Police Officer.

921
01:24:58,927 --> 01:25:03,137
Mom. Mom. I remember now.

922
01:25:03,598 --> 01:25:06,772
I didn't want to join them.

923
01:25:07,335 --> 01:25:09,372
But Glen had a knife on me.

924
01:25:10,271 --> 01:25:14,378
Amanda...
I left Amanda in the forest.

925
01:25:17,745 --> 01:25:19,349
Okay, we'll find her.

926
01:25:20,148 --> 01:25:21,525
He's turned around.

927
01:25:23,785 --> 01:25:24,923
Let's go.

928
01:25:37,332 --> 01:25:39,835
- Come on, son.
- Here, mom. This is it.

929
01:25:41,236 --> 01:25:44,410
I know Amanda's here.
I can feel it.

930
01:25:45,440 --> 01:25:47,784
She's been here for over a day.

931
01:25:47,842 --> 01:25:51,483
We need to find help.
I'll call for an ambulance.

932
01:25:53,248 --> 01:25:54,659
No signal.

933
01:25:58,219 --> 01:25:59,857
Rommel, there's no signal.

934
01:26:00,688 --> 01:26:04,101
Mom, you need to go home.
Go and ask for help.

935
01:26:04,159 --> 01:26:09,700
- I'm not leaving you like this.
- Mom, mom, mom. I got this.

936
01:26:10,064 --> 01:26:12,874
Amanda needs us, Mom.

937
01:26:12,934 --> 01:26:15,676
I can't. I can't leave you, Rommel.

938
01:26:16,504 --> 01:26:18,916
Stay here.

939
01:26:33,688 --> 01:26:38,296
- Rommel! Rommel!
- Mom, I'll be fine. Go home.

940
01:26:38,359 --> 01:26:40,965
Call for help. it'll be alright.

941
01:26:41,896 --> 01:26:43,273
Be careful, mom.

942
01:26:51,639 --> 01:26:52,913
Amanda!

943
01:27:09,390 --> 01:27:10,869
Amanda!

944
01:27:14,229 --> 01:27:15,230
Amanda!

945
01:27:39,087 --> 01:27:40,828
Brother, please help me.

946
01:27:51,699 --> 01:27:55,340
Rommel. Let's practice.

947
01:27:57,005 --> 01:28:01,715
Fifteen steps forward.
Three to the left.

948
01:28:04,612 --> 01:28:05,989
Thank you.

949
01:28:08,583 --> 01:28:09,960
Thank you, brother.

950
01:28:45,853 --> 01:28:47,355
Please don't die on me.

951
01:28:56,464 --> 01:28:57,272
Rommel.

952
01:28:58,966 --> 01:29:00,104
Rommel.

953
01:29:01,669 --> 01:29:03,615
Rommel, show yourself.

954
01:29:05,106 --> 01:29:06,551
Stop hiding.

955
01:29:11,813 --> 01:29:12,917
Amanda!

956
01:29:14,982 --> 01:29:17,588
Amanda. Amanda. Amanda.

957
01:29:19,287 --> 01:29:22,097
Amanda. Amanda.

958
01:29:22,957 --> 01:29:27,565
Amanda. Amanda.
Amanda, wake up! it's Rommel.

959
01:29:30,198 --> 01:29:31,700
Amanda.

960
01:29:36,604 --> 01:29:39,710
- Amanda.
- Rommel.

961
01:29:42,276 --> 01:29:44,017
You came back for me.

962
01:29:48,716 --> 01:29:52,425
I can't move.

963
01:29:57,225 --> 01:29:59,728
You're bleeding, Rommel.

964
01:30:03,631 --> 01:30:05,167
Just leave me.

965
01:30:05,233 --> 01:30:09,545
- I will not leave you, Amanda.
- Please, go. Save yourself.

966
01:30:09,604 --> 01:30:11,811
Rommel didn't leave Amanda.

967
01:30:12,774 --> 01:30:17,723
They grew old and
had many children, remember?

968
01:30:18,079 --> 01:30:20,116
Twenty-seven kids.

969
01:30:21,249 --> 01:30:25,163
Can you take that? Huh?

970
01:30:28,656 --> 01:30:33,332
Amanda. Amanda!
Amanda, wake up! Amanda!

971
01:30:35,863 --> 01:30:37,274
Sir, somebody's in there.

972
01:30:39,033 --> 01:30:40,205
Help!

973
01:30:40,968 --> 01:30:45,075
Sir, please help us!
Sir! Please!

974
01:30:46,007 --> 01:30:50,149
- Get away from there!
- Sir, I'm innocent.

975
01:30:50,211 --> 01:30:51,849
Sir, we need help.

976
01:30:51,913 --> 01:30:55,383
- Sir, please, help us.
- Check the girl. Go.

977
01:30:59,720 --> 01:31:00,926
Sir, she's alive.

978
01:31:02,723 --> 01:31:04,828
- We need your help.
- Call an ambulance. Quickly!

979
01:31:05,193 --> 01:31:06,194
Yes, Sir.

980
01:31:09,030 --> 01:31:10,668
Amanda. Amanda.

981
01:31:25,379 --> 01:31:26,517
Rommel!

982
01:31:30,718 --> 01:31:35,758
Rommel! Show yourself.

983
01:31:36,757 --> 01:31:38,134
Rommel, come out!

984
01:31:38,559 --> 01:31:41,768
Sir, thank you for responding
quickly to my mother's call.

985
01:31:41,829 --> 01:31:43,240
Thank you.

986
01:31:43,297 --> 01:31:45,072
Your mother didn't call me.

987
01:31:45,933 --> 01:31:48,311
Aren't you friends with William?
Where is he?

988
01:31:48,469 --> 01:31:50,210
Sir, he's not my friend.

989
01:31:50,404 --> 01:31:52,543
Sir, he's behind all of this.

990
01:31:55,810 --> 01:31:58,381
Reyes? Reyes, what's your status?

991
01:31:58,646 --> 01:32:03,288
Reyes, What's your status?

992
01:32:10,658 --> 01:32:12,569
Sir, what's going on?

993
01:32:12,627 --> 01:32:13,833
Reyes isn't answering.

994
01:32:13,895 --> 01:32:16,136
Bring them to the hospital.
I'll go to the pension house. Go.

995
01:32:16,797 --> 01:32:17,639
Hold on!

996
01:32:28,376 --> 01:32:33,553
Rosa.
Where are you going?

997
01:32:34,248 --> 01:32:36,250
I'm coming to get you.

998
01:32:36,851 --> 01:32:38,694
Rosa.

999
01:33:11,319 --> 01:33:13,299
- Please hand me the gauze.
- She's going into shock!

1000
01:33:13,588 --> 01:33:14,658
Sedate her.

1001
01:33:31,439 --> 01:33:35,444
Rosa, stop hiding Rommel.

1002
01:33:37,011 --> 01:33:38,854
Where is your son?

1003
01:33:44,785 --> 01:33:46,662
Sir, please don't move.

1004
01:33:47,722 --> 01:33:50,669
Please don't move.

1005
01:33:54,095 --> 01:33:56,541
- I need you to steady, Sir.
- Hello.

1006
01:33:56,597 --> 01:34:00,739
Hello, mom?
I'm with Amanda now.

1007
01:34:01,502 --> 01:34:02,412
She's still alive.

1008
01:34:03,004 --> 01:34:05,109
But We need to bring her
to the hospital.

1009
01:34:05,973 --> 01:34:08,920
- Hello, Mom? Mom?
- Rommel...

1010
01:34:09,677 --> 01:34:11,987
Rommel, William is here.

1011
01:34:13,781 --> 01:34:17,593
Sir. Sir. Sir, we need to go back.
My mom's in trouble. Please.

1012
01:34:17,652 --> 01:34:19,188
No, Rommel.

1013
01:34:19,587 --> 01:34:21,828
- Turn around, please.
- No, Rommel. Don't come back.

1014
01:34:21,989 --> 01:34:26,870
- Sir, my mom will die, please.
- You are not going back here, Rommel!

1015
01:34:27,395 --> 01:34:28,635
Don't come back.

1016
01:34:28,729 --> 01:34:30,333
Your mom or your girlfriend?

1017
01:34:30,398 --> 01:34:34,175
- You're still bleeding. It's not good.
- Son. My Son, listen to me.

1018
01:34:34,635 --> 01:34:38,708
You will not come back here.
You don't have to choose.

1019
01:34:39,540 --> 01:34:41,577
Just go straight to the hospital.

1020
01:34:42,410 --> 01:34:43,753
I'll handle this.

1021
01:34:44,945 --> 01:34:47,084
You will never be able to run
to the Police now!

1022
01:34:47,248 --> 01:34:48,556
I love you.

1023
01:34:51,886 --> 01:34:53,126
I love you, mom.

1024
01:34:54,121 --> 01:34:55,293
Open the door!

1025
01:35:07,668 --> 01:35:09,511
Do you think you can escape me?

1026
01:35:16,977 --> 01:35:20,015
Stand up!
Where's Rommel? Stand up!

1027
01:35:20,081 --> 01:35:21,685
You bitch!
You just had to mess with me.

1028
01:35:21,749 --> 01:35:23,854
- Where's your son?
-I don't know!

1029
01:35:23,984 --> 01:35:24,758
You don't know?

1030
01:35:30,291 --> 01:35:32,271
- Stand up!
- Let me go.

